
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title> Border Width </title>
	<style type="text/css">
	.example-00{ 
		border-width: 5px; 
	} /* without border-style, border will not show up*/
	
	.example-01{ 
		border-style:solid;
	}
	
	.example-02{
		border-width: 5px;
		border-style:solid; 
	}
	
	.example-03{ 
		border-top-width:10px; 
		border-right-width:25px;
		border-bottom-width:10px;
		border-left-width:25px;
		border-style:solid; 
	}
	
	.example-04{
		border-width:10px 25px;
		border-style:solid;
	}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
    <h3>CSS border Example: The border-width Property </h3>
	
	<p><b>Note:</b> The "border-width" property does not work if it is used alone. Use the "border-style" property to set the borders first.</p>

    <p class="example-00">
		<mark>.example-00 { border-width: 5px; } </mark><br /><br />
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor
    </p>
    <p class="example-01">
		<mark>.example-01 { border-style:solid; } /* 3px default width on all sides */</mark><br /><br />
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor
    </p>
    <p class="example-02">
		<mark>.example-02 { border-width: 5px; border-style:solid; }</mark> <br /><br />
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor
    </p>
    <p class="example-03">
		<mark>.example-03 { border-top-width:10px; border-right-width:25px; border-bottom-width:10px; border-left-width:25px;
					 border-style:solid; }</mark><br /><br />
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor
    </p>
    <p class="example-04">
		<mark>.example-04 { border-width:10px 25px;
                  border-style:solid; } /* Shortcut - top - right - bottom - left */</mark><br /><br />
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor
    </p>

</body>

</html>


*배운것 :
1. solid는 boader에서의 선, dotted나 double과는 다르게 끊기지않는 선을나타냄.
2. <mark>태그를 사용하면 형광펜으로 칠한 효과를 나타낼수있다.
